id":"recUeHSn6y9W1xVLI","ref":"Exod.23.2","text":"Thou shalt not follow a multitude to do evil; neither shalt thou speak in a cause to decline after many to wrest judgment:","year":-1491},{"id":"rec16JGmNQaUISxPN","ref":"Exod.23.3","text":"Neither shalt thou countenance a poor man in his cause.","year":-1491},{"id":"recRdyemKfKphp0BI","ref":"Exod.23.4","text":"If thou meet thine enemy’s ox or his ass going astray, thou shalt surely bring it back to him again.","year":-1491},{"id":"rec1d6xVbKLBeLFgR","ref":"Exod.23.5","text":"If thou see the ass of him that hateth thee lying under his burden, and wouldest forbear to help him, thou shalt surely help with him.","year":-1491},{"id":"recGxkgSHeCrbl3vT","ref":"Exod.23.6","text":"Thou shalt not wrest the judgment of thy poor in his cause.","year":-1491},{"id":"recSdFWWW2EryFSRW","ref":"Exod.23.7","text":"Keep thee far from a false matter; and the innocent and righteous slay thou not: for I will not justify the wicked.","year":-1491},{"id":"recsXH8BDE6Fa1X01","ref":"Exod.23.8","text":"And thou shalt take no gift: for the gift blindeth the wise, and perverteth the words of the righteous.","year":-1491}]}
